1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:11,160
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo ovdje radi dva razloga. Prvi je razlog da bi smo došli u kontakt s Bogom,

2
00:00:11,160 --> 00:00:20,660
[SPEAKER_00] drugi rečimo da bi nas Bog izliječio i oslobodio. A drugi razlog je o tome da bi smo došli u kontakt s drugim ljudima.

3
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ako hoćeš ozdraviti do kraja, onda nije dosta sam lići k Bogu i moliti ga da te ozdravi,

4
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:33,359
[SPEAKER_00] nego moraš početi voljeti druge da bi ozdravio.

5
00:00:33,359 --> 00:00:39,899
[SPEAKER_00] Mi u agioterapiji imamo jednu posebnu terapiju. Zove se Agape terapija.

6
00:00:39,899 --> 00:00:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je terapija Božanskom ljubavlju gdje pacijent upija Božju bezuvjetnu ljubav i nježnost.

7
00:00:49,039 --> 00:00:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] I dok upija, on se liječi.

8
00:00:52,259 --> 00:00:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, taj lijek ne može ostati, to zdravlje ne može učvrstiti.

9
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:00,240
[SPEAKER_00] Nekod pacijent sada ne počne voljeti druge.

10
00:01:01,859 --> 00:01:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nije ljubav samo u tome da te netko voli,

11
00:01:06,599 --> 00:01:11,620
[SPEAKER_00] nego da nakon toga što te netko voli, ti počneš voljeti nekog drugoga.

12
00:01:13,719 --> 00:01:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav naime je samo do pola u tebi ako tebe samo netko voli.

13
00:01:19,159 --> 00:01:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] A ljubavlju se potpuno ispunjaš kad ti nekoga voliš.

14
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:31,700
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kad tebe netko voli onda si siguran, onda se osjećaš ta ti je egzistencija sigurno.

15
00:01:31,700 --> 00:01:35,200
[SPEAKER_00] Kad znaš da te Bog voli, onda znaš siguran se bit će sve dobro.

16
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:42,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ima bezbroj ljudi koji tebi trebaju, gdje tvoje srce čezne za njima, gdje bih tio s njima razgovarati,

17
00:01:42,219 --> 00:01:43,939
[SPEAKER_00] Htio bi im pomoć, htio bi biti uz njih.

18
00:01:43,939 --> 00:01:49,959
[SPEAKER_00] I ako nikoga ne voliš, osjećaš se frustriranim i besmislenim.

19
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] Drugim rječima, Božja ljubav ulazi u tebe i voli te,

20
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:58,959
[SPEAKER_00] ali ti još ne transcendiraš, još ne nadilaziš sebe.

21
00:01:58,959 --> 00:02:05,060
[SPEAKER_00] Kad počneš ljubiti drugog, tad si nadišao sebe, tad si zaboravio sebe i tad postaješ zdrav.

22
00:02:09,379 --> 00:02:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] Bezbrojni su ljudi koji ne mogu opraštati drugima. Zašto?

23
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:19,300
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što neprestano upijaju Božju ljubav i stano traže da ih netko voli.

24
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:23,120
[SPEAKER_00] A oni nisu nikada počeli voljeti druge.

25
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:33,099
[SPEAKER_00] Jer u tebe se izlije neka ljepota, nešto duboko i snažno i neka nježnost,

26
00:02:33,099 --> 00:02:36,120
[SPEAKER_00] onda kad nekoga voliš. Sjetiš i samo kad vidiš malo djete,

27
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] pa kad ga zagrliš, pa ga počneš ljubiti.

28
00:02:39,379 --> 00:02:43,360
[SPEAKER_00] Pa vodiš ga na ruku, a ono, djete, klikće, a tvoje srce igra.

29
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:46,919
[SPEAKER_00] I ako ti toga ne imaš, ti onda ne osjećaš ljubav.

30
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kad roditelji samo vole djete,

31
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] neizmjerno ga vole i razmazde ga,

32
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:57,319
[SPEAKER_00] to znači vežu uz sebe,

33
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] tada djete postaje bolesto.

34
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:01,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo duhoru, nego i psihički.

35
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:06,379
[SPEAKER_00] jer djete vapi da nekoga i ono voli.

36
00:03:06,379 --> 00:03:09,120
[SPEAKER_00] Da ide k drugima.

37
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:15,740
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako imate punu čašu, onda je čaša nesretna što ima tko popiti.

38
00:03:18,139 --> 00:03:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kad imaš čokoladu, pa i sam pojedeš,

39
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] to je najveća nesrća što ti se može dogoditi.

40
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] A kad ti nju podijeliš, ona je stostruko slađa.

41
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,599
[SPEAKER_00] Probajte, pa ćete vidjeti.

42
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:31,819
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je to tako?

43
00:03:31,819 --> 00:03:35,580
[SPEAKER_00] Pa shvatite, zato što je čovjek stvoren na sliku Božu.

44
00:03:35,580 --> 00:03:39,639
[SPEAKER_00] A slika Boža je da Bog nije jedan i sam,

45
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] nego jedan u trojici.

46
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] To su tri osobe koje se vole ludo.

47
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:50,699
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome, jer čovjek na tu sliku ne može drugačije nego voljeti.

48
00:03:50,699 --> 00:03:54,479
[SPEAKER_00] I on je nesretan i bolestan dok nekoga ne voli.

49
00:03:57,759 --> 00:04:03,060
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto smo rekli onda da tko ne oprašta neće nikad postati zdrav,

50
00:04:03,060 --> 00:04:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] čak ni fizički.

51
00:04:04,199 --> 00:04:06,080
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo zato.

52
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dok ti nekom ne opraštaš, ti će imati dovoljno razloga

53
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,419
[SPEAKER_00] da ti se ni jedan čovjek ne svidi.

54
00:04:12,419 --> 00:04:18,959
[SPEAKER_00] Tek kad počneš opraštati zato što ti se ne sviđaju ljudi,

55
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,319
[SPEAKER_00] što ti nisu simpatični.

56
00:04:20,319 --> 00:04:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kad počneš opraštati, od jedan puta ćeš ti se pogled otvoriti

57
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] za ono vječno, duboko u ljudima,

58
00:04:25,699 --> 00:04:27,660
[SPEAKER_00] zaljubit ćeš se u svakog čovjeka,

59
00:04:27,660 --> 00:04:28,740
[SPEAKER_00] osobito u siromaka,

60
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:34,540
[SPEAKER_00] osobito u jadnog pijanca koji sad prljavi kakav sve ne.

61
00:04:34,540 --> 00:04:37,680
[SPEAKER_00] Zaljubit ćeš se da ćeš vijeti nego u dušu iznutra.

62
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:40,839
[SPEAKER_00] I tad kad zavoliš dušu, tad oseće da si sretan.

63
00:04:40,839 --> 00:04:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tad počinje nebo.

64
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] Bezbroj ljudi idu u molitvene grupe,

65
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:49,060
[SPEAKER_00] idu na sve moguće seminare,

66
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:51,879
[SPEAKER_00] obavljaju duhone vježbe,

67
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:58,279
[SPEAKER_00] a uvijek su jednako nesretni, frustrirani,

68
00:04:58,279 --> 00:05:00,060
[SPEAKER_00] besmisleni, jadni.

69
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ima ljudi koji idu svake nedelje i svaki dan na misu,

70
00:05:06,420 --> 00:05:08,680
[SPEAKER_00] ali ništa, ni koraka nisu krenuti.

71
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] Čim mi izađu s mise,

72
00:05:09,579 --> 00:05:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] ta, ta, ta, ta, ogovor, ogovor, ogovor.

73
00:05:13,740 --> 00:05:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jer si glavno susjed,

74
00:05:14,519 --> 00:05:15,379
[SPEAKER_00] daj svi ide ovog župnika,

75
00:05:15,379 --> 00:05:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] oj kakav ja, pa kak se danas obuka,

76
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:18,259
[SPEAKER_00] pa gled kako ono priše nos,

77
00:05:18,259 --> 00:05:19,740
[SPEAKER_00] pa svi ide kakav mu frizura danas stoji.

78
00:05:19,740 --> 00:05:21,139
[SPEAKER_00] I gotovo je.

79
00:05:21,139 --> 00:05:27,259
[SPEAKER_00] Jer svaka negativna pomisa o tebe dijeli od drugih ljudi.

80
00:05:27,259 --> 00:05:31,100
[SPEAKER_00] I to ne samo da se dijeliš od župnika,

81
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,060
[SPEAKER_00] što se njega kritizira,

82
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] no da se dijeliš i od vjernika,

83
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:34,199
[SPEAKER_00] da više nikom ne možeš poglatožiti,

84
00:05:34,199 --> 00:05:35,040
[SPEAKER_00] sad si ti ljud,

85
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:37,720
[SPEAKER_00] jer u tebi zlo i negativnost i mrak.

86
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:45,540
[SPEAKER_00] Zato nemoguće je bilo koga zavoljeti da mu ne praštaš.

87
00:05:45,540 --> 00:05:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad praštaš, ti dopuštaš njemu da dođe k tebi,

88
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,959
[SPEAKER_00] tad ga vidiš izbliza i tada ga zavoliš

89
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:54,560
[SPEAKER_00] i tada si prešao zapravo granicu ljudskoga.

90
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:57,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tad si sa zemaljskog ušao na nebesko.

91
00:05:57,019 --> 00:05:59,100
[SPEAKER_00] Tad si od ljudskog ušao na božansko.

92
00:05:59,100 --> 00:06:02,680
[SPEAKER_00] Tada si sretan i tad postaješ zdrav.

93
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:07,180
[SPEAKER_00] To je opasno ste uvijek i hagioterapije,

94
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo hagioterapeuta ako ne zna tu bitnu činjenicu,

95
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:13,819
[SPEAKER_00] pa ako stalno, stalno napaja ljude božom ljubavu,

96
00:06:13,819 --> 00:06:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] božom ljubavu i vidi da ne uspjeva,

97
00:06:15,579 --> 00:06:16,639
[SPEAKER_00] neće daći daleko.

98
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:20,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ti moraš pacijentu isto vremeno pomoći,

99
00:06:20,259 --> 00:06:22,040
[SPEAKER_00] jednak počne nekoga voljeti.

100
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:24,579
[SPEAKER_00] Dok mu dadeš samo malo ljubavi,

101
00:06:24,579 --> 00:06:26,139
[SPEAKER_00] sad ju nauči, idi praštati.

102
00:06:26,139 --> 00:06:28,120
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš li voljeti majku,

103
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,379
[SPEAKER_00] možeš voljeti oca,

104
00:06:29,379 --> 00:06:30,399
[SPEAKER_00] možeš ovoga ili onoga.

105
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:36,459
[SPEAKER_00] Tek kad počneš voljeti nekoga bit će zdrav.

106
00:06:36,459 --> 00:06:36,819
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

107
00:06:36,899 --> 00:06:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dok nego ti ne oprašaš i ne voliš onoga koji tebe mrzi,

108
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:43,759
[SPEAKER_00] dota će taj ispijati sve tvoje snage.

109
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] Poznam ljude koji u obitelji ne mogu trpjeti svoju,

110
00:06:48,079 --> 00:06:51,180
[SPEAKER_00] ni oca, ni majku, ni sestru, ni nikoga.

111
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:51,600
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

112
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:55,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ti uvijek prigovara, uvijek ti neko prigovara.

113
00:06:55,860 --> 00:06:57,660
[SPEAKER_00] Prigovori ti sesa, prigovori žena,

114
00:06:57,660 --> 00:06:59,439
[SPEAKER_00] prigovori djete, prigovori punica,

115
00:06:59,439 --> 00:07:00,399
[SPEAKER_00] prigovori sve krva.

116
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:02,660
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su nesretni, šta rade?

117
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] Prestano se dijele, idemo mužu od ove moje sve krve,

118
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:07,879
[SPEAKER_00] to više ne može se.

119
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:10,240
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo ženo od ove lude punice, ne može izdržati.

120
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:14,279
[SPEAKER_00] I ti moraš se, ideš, bježi, bježi, bježi.

121
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo od majke, ne mogu već to trpjeti,

122
00:07:16,019 --> 00:07:16,779
[SPEAKER_00] stalno me opominje.

123
00:07:16,779 --> 00:07:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo te sestre poludile.

124
00:07:19,540 --> 00:07:21,620
[SPEAKER_00] Tu nije rješenje, prijatelji dragi.

125
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:24,339
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo se rastaviti u braku, ne mogu više s tobom.

126
00:07:24,339 --> 00:07:25,459
[SPEAKER_00] Tu nije rješenje.

127
00:07:25,459 --> 00:07:27,740
[SPEAKER_00] Samo ćeš biti još bolesniji.

128
00:07:27,740 --> 00:07:29,779
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedna bolest i rana na drugu.

129
00:07:29,779 --> 00:07:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo da se ne prestano opominjate,

130
00:07:33,079 --> 00:07:34,639
[SPEAKER_00] da li prestano se kritizirate,

131
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:37,839
[SPEAKER_00] da li prestano se sukobljavate, ranjavate, traumatizirate,

132
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:41,259
[SPEAKER_00] nego sad još odlazite i sad tek nastaje neizlječiva rana.

133
00:07:41,259 --> 00:07:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] Tek sad ste bolesti, najdublje.

134
00:07:48,180 --> 00:07:50,620
[SPEAKER_00] Bezbrojni ljudi, pogotovo jer dođe mi zlo,

135
00:07:50,620 --> 00:07:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] kad još kakviju terapeuti i počem govoriti,

136
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:54,620
[SPEAKER_00] pa rastavite se, šta ćete vidjeti da ne možete izdržati,

137
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:55,319
[SPEAKER_00] to je najgore.

138
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:57,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ti me ne liječiš više pacijenta.

139
00:07:57,399 --> 00:08:01,459
[SPEAKER_00] Ti moraš od njega zahvati od tog pacijenta,

140
00:08:01,459 --> 00:08:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] da on polako, polako uhvati od roda.

141
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo osjeti, znam dubine ovoga čovjeka

142
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji me mrazi mene vole.

143
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,279
[SPEAKER_00] I ti si se spasio.

144
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:09,959
[SPEAKER_00] Dubine njegove me vole.

145
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:13,079
[SPEAKER_00] I drugo, opraštam ti, jer te razumijem.

146
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,339
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam nija bolji.

147
00:08:16,339 --> 00:08:18,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ja tebe kritiziram.

148
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:20,459
[SPEAKER_00] Opraštam ti, opraštam, opraštam.

149
00:08:20,459 --> 00:08:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tad si nadišao sebe,

150
00:08:23,019 --> 00:08:24,279
[SPEAKER_00] tad si nadišao zlo,

151
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] tad te zlo više ne pogađa,

152
00:08:25,899 --> 00:08:26,959
[SPEAKER_00] jer si više iznad njega.

153
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:29,139
[SPEAKER_00] Tad ljubiš i tad si u nebu.

154
00:08:29,139 --> 00:08:30,339
[SPEAKER_00] Tad si sličan Bogu.

155
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:38,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ne postoji mogućnost da se izliječiš u svojoj duhovnoj duši.

156
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:41,580
[SPEAKER_00] U svojoj, u sebi kao osobi,

157
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:43,799
[SPEAKER_00] a da ne počneš voljeti druge.

158
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:48,120
[SPEAKER_00] Zato Isusa koji je htio pomoć čovjeku,

159
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,379
[SPEAKER_00] nije mogo drugačije nego da kaže

160
00:08:49,379 --> 00:08:51,360
[SPEAKER_00] ljubite svoje neprijatelje.

161
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dokle go ti mrziš neprijatelja,

162
00:08:54,559 --> 00:08:55,879
[SPEAKER_00] on tebe ranjava.

163
00:08:55,879 --> 00:08:58,120
[SPEAKER_00] Jer neprijatelj nije unaj koji te na kraju

164
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] sa kaljačnikovim ubija

165
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:02,559
[SPEAKER_00] i koji, ne znam kakve,

166
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] mine i granate baca na tebe.

167
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] Nije to, to je ono kranje,

168
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,600
[SPEAKER_00] to ubije malo tvoje tijelo,

169
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,179
[SPEAKER_00] to nije opasno.

170
00:09:07,179 --> 00:09:09,240
[SPEAKER_00] On tebe ubija već time što ti je neprijatelj.

171
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] On može biti danas u kini tvoj neprijatelj.

172
00:09:10,940 --> 00:09:12,700
[SPEAKER_00] Tebe muči, tu su granate,

173
00:09:12,700 --> 00:09:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] u tebe muči.

174
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,700
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoj mi ga spominjati,

175
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] užasaj, ne mogu govoriti o njemu.

176
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,580
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ćeš početi govoriti o njemu,

177
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] i vidiš, tvoje vrti, vrti, vrti.

178
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tvoja savjesta je izranjena,

179
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:22,240
[SPEAKER_00] tvoje srce je izranjeno,

180
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,919
[SPEAKER_00] tvoji želuda stvara

181
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:24,879
[SPEAKER_00] sve moguće

182
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:29,419
[SPEAKER_00] sve moguće čireve.

183
00:09:29,419 --> 00:09:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] Gotov si.

184
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:32,519
[SPEAKER_00] Stvar je tako jasno.

185
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] I nemamo drugog puta

186
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,100
[SPEAKER_00] nego početi ljubiti.

187
00:09:36,100 --> 00:09:40,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ali shvatite, ljubav je uvijek

188
00:09:40,779 --> 00:09:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] dvostruka, najprije pasivna.

189
00:09:42,779 --> 00:09:44,840
[SPEAKER_00] Najprije te ljubav rađa.

190
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,440
[SPEAKER_00] Primaš ljubav najprije.

191
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] Bog me voli, to je bitno.

192
00:09:49,059 --> 00:09:50,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ako toga nemaš, nećeš nikad početi

193
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:52,080
[SPEAKER_00] ljubiti, ne možeš ljubiti.

194
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,700
[SPEAKER_00] Jer tebe nema.

195
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:56,799
[SPEAKER_00] Najprije te Božja ljubav preporodi.

196
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:59,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ta ljubav sad može o sad,

197
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] sad ti ideš ljubiti,

198
00:10:01,059 --> 00:10:02,080
[SPEAKER_00] sad tom ljubavljom.

199
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,259
[SPEAKER_00] Sad si siguran.

200
00:10:03,259 --> 00:10:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] I sad te više niko ne može raniti.

201
00:10:05,019 --> 00:10:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] I sad si slobodan.

202
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:09,879
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko mi ljudi dolazi,

203
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:10,720
[SPEAKER_00] pa šta da radim,

204
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,100
[SPEAKER_00] pa ja to ne mogu više izdršati ovo,

205
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] kažem pa.

206
00:10:12,659 --> 00:10:14,899
[SPEAKER_00] I šta ćeš sad?

207
00:10:14,899 --> 00:10:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] Pa najrednji bi pobjegao.

208
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pobjegni i?

209
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ćeš da ti bježiš zajedno sa svojim neprijateljom.

210
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] On je u tebi.

211
00:10:23,059 --> 00:10:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] Nijedan neprijatelj nije izvan tebe.

212
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] Nemaš kamo pobjeći.

213
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:30,720
[SPEAKER_00] Bježi samo da te fizički ne rani.

214
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:33,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ali on doliko gore ono što te on iznutra već,

215
00:10:33,279 --> 00:10:34,120
[SPEAKER_00] ranjava, ranjava,

216
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:34,740
[SPEAKER_00] redi to dalje,

217
00:10:34,740 --> 00:10:35,320
[SPEAKER_00] traje.

218
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] Nemaš kamo pobjeći.

219
00:10:37,779 --> 00:10:38,679
[SPEAKER_00] Rasta ove brakovi,

220
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] užani si sa drugom.

221
00:10:39,539 --> 00:10:42,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ma kak je ona žena od prije koju si ostavio mučite?

222
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je u tebi čoveče.

223
00:10:43,639 --> 00:10:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] Tva savjez je nagrižena i nestaje mu.

224
00:10:46,460 --> 00:10:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] Užas ne hvata.

225
00:10:47,659 --> 00:10:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome,

226
00:10:50,019 --> 00:10:51,879
[SPEAKER_00] rješenje problema je samo

227
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:54,100
[SPEAKER_00] nadići to,

228
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] početvoljiti,

229
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,139
[SPEAKER_00] oprostiti

230
00:10:56,139 --> 00:10:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] i vidjeti da

231
00:10:58,559 --> 00:11:00,740
[SPEAKER_00] dubina u svakom čovjeku

232
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] su s tobom

233
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:03,600
[SPEAKER_00] u savjezu.

234
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:06,100
[SPEAKER_00] I možeš izliječiti svakog čovjeka.

235
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:07,460
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome,

236
00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:10,919
[SPEAKER_00] nije rješenje da bježiš od zla i od ljudi,

237
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:12,279
[SPEAKER_00] nego da zlo prihvatiš

238
00:11:12,279 --> 00:11:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] i da ga pobjediš.

239
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:16,340
[SPEAKER_00] Nije u tome da tražiš od drugi

240
00:11:16,340 --> 00:11:16,899
[SPEAKER_00] nek se mijenja.

241
00:11:16,899 --> 00:11:18,299
[SPEAKER_00] Moja žena me stalno kaže

242
00:11:18,299 --> 00:11:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] napadaj, više to ne mogu.

243
00:11:19,639 --> 00:11:20,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se ona ne promijeni,

244
00:11:20,659 --> 00:11:21,600
[SPEAKER_00] rekao šta što onda?

245
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:23,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se promijeri,

246
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:25,559
[SPEAKER_00] to nije biti ništa zdraviji ni bolji.

247
00:11:26,139 --> 00:11:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] jer u tebi je zlo.

248
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] Pa šta da napravim?

249
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,139
[SPEAKER_00] Promijeni se ti prema njoj.

250
00:11:32,139 --> 00:11:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] A, dosta mi je.

251
00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:34,639
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, onda kad je dosta,

252
00:11:34,639 --> 00:11:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] idi.

253
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kao je tu ispred tebe.

254
00:11:36,460 --> 00:11:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] Samo skoči.

255
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] To drugo treba učiti,

256
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,399
[SPEAKER_00] prijatelji dragi.

257
00:11:43,399 --> 00:11:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mi se možemo sastaviti ovde

258
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:49,919
[SPEAKER_00] još stotinu godina.

259
00:11:49,919 --> 00:11:51,419
[SPEAKER_00] Dok ne napravimo zajednice,

260
00:11:51,419 --> 00:11:52,840
[SPEAKER_00] dok mi ne budemo zajednice,

261
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,080
[SPEAKER_00] znači zajednice,

262
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,279
[SPEAKER_00] dok ti ne zavoliš neke ljude

263
00:11:55,279 --> 00:11:56,100
[SPEAKER_00] koji dolaze ovde,

264
00:11:56,139 --> 00:11:57,259
[SPEAKER_00] ti uzalu dolaziš.

265
00:11:57,259 --> 00:12:01,360
[SPEAKER_00] A zajedni šta?

266
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] Nije u tom da kažeš

267
00:12:02,059 --> 00:12:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] joj prvo se bračiće,

268
00:12:02,820 --> 00:12:03,720
[SPEAKER_00] lijepo nam govori.

269
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:05,379
[SPEAKER_00] Joj, fin, osjećam se tako,

270
00:12:05,379 --> 00:12:06,259
[SPEAKER_00] blaži dušu.

271
00:12:06,259 --> 00:12:07,379
[SPEAKER_00] Da, i onda kad izađeš van,

272
00:12:07,379 --> 00:12:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] neputa naletiš opet na one

273
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:11,620
[SPEAKER_00] koji ti odblažuju dušu.

274
00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:12,679
[SPEAKER_00] Koji te raje,

275
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:13,919
[SPEAKER_00] a joj, Ivančić,

276
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:15,120
[SPEAKER_00] u mojoj ništvinici napravi,

277
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] opet ja.

278
00:12:18,139 --> 00:12:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] ljubiti to dvostruko znači,

279
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] voljen sam,

280
00:12:25,659 --> 00:12:27,419
[SPEAKER_00] ja imam pravo živjeti,

281
00:12:27,419 --> 00:12:28,879
[SPEAKER_00] a voljen sam znači,

282
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:30,240
[SPEAKER_00] nisam ugrožen,

283
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,620
[SPEAKER_00] ja se ne bojim,

284
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] mene niko ne može ugroziti.

285
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se ne bojim,

286
00:12:35,179 --> 00:12:35,799
[SPEAKER_00] ja se ne bojim.

287
00:12:35,799 --> 00:12:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] Mene je Bog ludo voli.

288
00:12:37,659 --> 00:12:39,740
[SPEAKER_00] A Bog je apsolutno samodobar.

289
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,139
[SPEAKER_00] I u tome najprije moraš se

290
00:12:41,139 --> 00:12:42,559
[SPEAKER_00] otopiti, uživati,

291
00:12:42,559 --> 00:12:43,259
[SPEAKER_00] roditi se.

292
00:12:43,259 --> 00:12:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kada si ukadi i uživaš

293
00:12:45,039 --> 00:12:45,879
[SPEAKER_00] u Bože ljubavi?

294
00:12:45,879 --> 00:12:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] To najprije moraš.

295
00:12:46,820 --> 00:12:47,700
[SPEAKER_00] Natopiti se moraš,

296
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:48,820
[SPEAKER_00] balzamirati,

297
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:50,720
[SPEAKER_00] amalgamirati jednostavno u sebi,

298
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,340
[SPEAKER_00] natopiti,

299
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:52,860
[SPEAKER_00] prožeti se jednostavno

300
00:12:52,860 --> 00:12:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] Božom ljubavi.

301
00:12:53,460 --> 00:12:55,299
[SPEAKER_00] E sad kad je to proželo,

302
00:12:55,299 --> 00:12:56,419
[SPEAKER_00] sad gledate,

303
00:12:56,419 --> 00:12:57,320
[SPEAKER_00] možeš li voljeti?

304
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ne možeš,

305
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:58,299
[SPEAKER_00] onda kažeš,

306
00:12:58,340 --> 00:12:59,100
[SPEAKER_00] joj Bože, još malo.

307
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:01,100
[SPEAKER_00] Napiješ još jednu čašu

308
00:13:01,100 --> 00:13:01,700
[SPEAKER_00] o njegove ljubavi.

309
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:02,279
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ide.

310
00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] Joj, još malo.

311
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:06,919
[SPEAKER_00] Je, sad mogu da iso.

312
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ste?

313
00:13:07,639 --> 00:13:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] Onda počneš,

314
00:13:09,559 --> 00:13:10,860
[SPEAKER_00] tebe volim i tebe volim.

315
00:13:10,860 --> 00:13:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] Gledaš, joj ona me gnjavi.

316
00:13:12,220 --> 00:13:13,139
[SPEAKER_00] Joj, baš te volim.

317
00:13:13,139 --> 00:13:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] I ona mi je gadan.

318
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Baš me volim.

319
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ona nesimpatičan.

320
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] Što mi je drag.

321
00:13:17,059 --> 00:13:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dođi.

322
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:23,759
[SPEAKER_00] I ona ljubiš ježeve,

323
00:13:23,759 --> 00:13:24,399
