324
00:13:24,399 --> 00:13:27,440
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš ježa poljubiti bez brige.

325
00:13:28,299 --> 00:13:29,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bode više.

326
00:13:29,100 --> 00:13:33,799
[SPEAKER_00] Hajdemo na taj put.

327
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo na prvi korak.

328
00:13:36,139 --> 00:13:39,259
[SPEAKER_00] Napunit se Bože ljubavi.

329
00:13:39,259 --> 00:13:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pustiti Isusa u tebe

330
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:42,100
[SPEAKER_00] da te ljubi.

331
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:44,159
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste vi zapamtili

332
00:13:44,159 --> 00:13:45,679
[SPEAKER_00] koji su ono šest točaka

333
00:13:45,679 --> 00:13:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] molitve da biste mogli?

334
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,919
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste zbilja?

335
00:13:48,919 --> 00:13:51,120
[SPEAKER_00] Prva točka, dakle,

336
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:53,519
[SPEAKER_00] odluči se da hoćeš biti zbogom,

337
00:13:53,519 --> 00:13:54,240
[SPEAKER_00] da hođeš moliti.

338
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:54,679
[SPEAKER_00] To je prvo.

339
00:13:58,259 --> 00:14:07,600
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo, stani

340
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:09,139
[SPEAKER_00] na razinu duha.

341
00:14:09,139 --> 00:14:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] Na onu razinu

342
00:14:10,679 --> 00:14:11,820
[SPEAKER_00] gdje si ti kao čovjek

343
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] od Boga stvoren

344
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:14,139
[SPEAKER_00] na sliku Bože.

345
00:14:14,139 --> 00:14:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] Podsjeti se

346
00:14:15,639 --> 00:14:16,259
[SPEAKER_00] tko si.

347
00:14:19,059 --> 00:14:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] od Boga izlaziš,

348
00:14:20,519 --> 00:14:21,799
[SPEAKER_00] k Bogu ideš.

349
00:14:21,799 --> 00:14:24,279
[SPEAKER_00] U Bogu zavisi

350
00:14:24,279 --> 00:14:25,500
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli tvoj život.

351
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] Tvoja sudbina

352
00:14:27,220 --> 00:14:28,120
[SPEAKER_00] u njegovim rukama.

353
00:14:34,399 --> 00:14:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] I sad na toj razini

354
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:36,759
[SPEAKER_00] duha načini

355
00:14:36,759 --> 00:14:37,740
[SPEAKER_00] znak križa.

356
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:39,299
[SPEAKER_00] Prije tom troje,

357
00:14:39,299 --> 00:14:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] misliš,

358
00:14:39,759 --> 00:14:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] to je Isusov križ.

359
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] To mene oslobađa.

360
00:14:42,460 --> 00:14:43,620
[SPEAKER_00] To je presjeto

361
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] trojstvo na meni.

362
00:14:56,860 --> 00:14:57,360
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro,

363
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:58,159
[SPEAKER_00] ga činom dobro

364
00:14:58,159 --> 00:14:59,179
[SPEAKER_00] pravite znak križa.

365
00:14:59,179 --> 00:15:00,440
[SPEAKER_00] Neki malo požurjem

366
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,320
[SPEAKER_00] sa svim to svetogamen,

367
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:01,879
[SPEAKER_00] onda to nije.

368
00:15:01,879 --> 00:15:02,899
[SPEAKER_00] Baš je važno

369
00:15:02,899 --> 00:15:03,779
[SPEAKER_00] meditativno.

370
00:15:03,779 --> 00:15:04,860
[SPEAKER_00] Baš nako polako

371
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:05,580
[SPEAKER_00] u ime Otca

372
00:15:05,580 --> 00:15:07,419
[SPEAKER_00] i Sina

373
00:15:07,419 --> 00:15:09,899
[SPEAKER_00] i Duha

374
00:15:09,899 --> 00:15:11,779
[UNKNOWN] Svetoga.

375
00:15:11,779 --> 00:15:15,080
[SPEAKER_00] Tada osjetiš da duša,

376
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,059
[SPEAKER_00] jer duša ne može

377
00:15:16,059 --> 00:15:16,860
[SPEAKER_00] tako brzo

378
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:17,779
