379
00:15:17,779 --> 00:15:18,279
[SPEAKER_00] veći duša

380
00:15:18,279 --> 00:15:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] treba malo vremena

381
00:15:19,159 --> 00:15:19,820
[SPEAKER_00] da doživi

382
00:15:19,820 --> 00:15:20,720
