384
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,879
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se ispuni

385
00:15:22,879 --> 00:15:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] čitavim

386
00:15:24,220 --> 00:15:25,700
[SPEAKER_00] sadržajem

387
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:26,720
[SPEAKER_00] znaka križa.

388
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:32,299
[SPEAKER_00] Četvrta točka.

389
00:15:32,299 --> 00:15:34,940
[SPEAKER_00] Otvori Isusu vratare.

390
00:15:35,100 --> 00:15:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse, dođi

391
