392
00:15:36,879 --> 00:15:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] Otvorio si mu.

393
00:15:51,639 --> 00:15:54,679
[SPEAKER_00] I sada kao najboljeg prijatelja

394
00:15:54,679 --> 00:15:55,320
[SPEAKER_00] možeš ga pustiti

395
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,240
[SPEAKER_00] u sve odaje,

396
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,220
[SPEAKER_00] u sve prostore

397
00:15:57,220 --> 00:15:57,860
[SPEAKER_00] svoje duše

398
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] i svoga života.

399
00:15:58,559 --> 00:15:59,279
[SPEAKER_00] Rekneš mu Isuse,

400
00:15:59,279 --> 00:16:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] molim te dođi,

401
00:16:00,039 --> 00:16:00,580
[SPEAKER_00] pogledaj.

402
00:16:00,580 --> 00:16:02,700
[SPEAKER_00] Izliječi ono što je ranjeno,

403
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:04,259
[SPEAKER_00] oprosti ono što je prljavo

404
00:16:04,259 --> 00:16:05,179
[SPEAKER_00] i grešno.

405
00:16:05,179 --> 00:16:08,840
[SPEAKER_00] Budi u meni Isusa.

406
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:09,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ti samo gledaj

407
00:16:09,759 --> 00:16:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] kako Isus

408
00:16:10,539 --> 00:16:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] mijenja

409
00:16:11,259 --> 00:16:12,379
[SPEAKER_00] tvoju nutrinju.

410
00:16:12,379 --> 00:16:14,220
[SPEAKER_00] Tvoje misli,

411
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:14,840
[SPEAKER_00] osjećaje,

412
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,919
[SPEAKER_00] doživljaje,

413
00:16:15,919 --> 00:16:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] cijelu tvoju prošlosti.

414
00:16:17,159 --> 00:16:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] Sve tvoje strahove.

415
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] Isus sve pregledava

416
00:16:21,059 --> 00:16:21,299
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

417
00:16:21,299 --> 00:16:22,259
[SPEAKER_00] ovo ćemo urediti,

418
00:16:22,259 --> 00:16:22,779
[SPEAKER_00] ovo ćemo.

419
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:24,639
[SPEAKER_00] Isus pravi u tebi red.

420
00:16:24,639 --> 00:16:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] I peto je onda zagrli mu noge

421
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:33,759
[SPEAKER_00] i reci Isuse,

422
00:16:33,759 --> 00:16:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] ostane sa mnom.

423
00:16:35,059 --> 00:16:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sve će biti dobro.

424
00:16:40,980 --> 00:16:42,179
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj više nikada

425
00:16:42,179 --> 00:16:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] od mene otići.

426
00:16:43,220 --> 00:16:47,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam da li vi razumijete

427
00:16:47,340 --> 00:16:48,620
[SPEAKER_00] kako to treba načiniti,

428
00:16:48,620 --> 00:16:50,080
[SPEAKER_00] jer vidim da mnogi ne znaju,

429
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:50,860
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno ne znaju

430
00:16:50,860 --> 00:16:51,620
[SPEAKER_00] kut bi sa tom

431
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] tabletom

432
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:53,899
[SPEAKER_00] kojim ja pokažem

433
00:16:53,899 --> 00:16:55,379
[SPEAKER_00] ili kut bi sa tom injekcijom,

434
00:16:55,379 --> 00:16:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] gdje bi bacili van

435
00:16:56,940 --> 00:16:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] ili u usta

436
00:16:57,559 --> 00:16:58,639
[SPEAKER_00] ili u žilu.

437
00:16:58,639 --> 00:17:01,600
[SPEAKER_00] Treba da je točno znat

438
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,279
[SPEAKER_00] kako se to raje.

439
00:17:02,279 --> 00:17:03,580
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kad reknem

440
00:17:03,580 --> 00:17:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo se odlučiti za molitvo.

441
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,740
[SPEAKER_00] Da ti zaista moraš stati,

442
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] mirosec,

443
00:17:07,619 --> 00:17:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] zato ako treba zatvoriti oči,

444
00:17:09,059 --> 00:17:09,740
[SPEAKER_00] reknemš Isuse,

445
00:17:09,740 --> 00:17:11,640
[SPEAKER_00] odlučujem se da ću sad biti s tobom.

446
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ili Bože,

447
00:17:13,579 --> 00:17:15,240
[SPEAKER_00] ja sad oću biti s tobom.

448
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ti to moraš reći.

449
00:17:16,259 --> 00:17:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ne moraš u ustim,

450
00:17:18,319 --> 00:17:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali srce,

451
00:17:19,460 --> 00:17:20,480
[SPEAKER_00] tiho u sebi,

452
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:21,140
[SPEAKER_00] ti to moraš reći.

453
00:17:21,140 --> 00:17:22,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to ne kažeš,

454
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] nije se ništo godilo.

455
00:17:23,019 --> 00:17:23,759
[SPEAKER_00] Pazi,

456
00:17:23,759 --> 00:17:25,160
[SPEAKER_00] tek tvoja riječ,

457
00:17:25,259 --> 00:17:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] tvoja odluka.

458
00:17:26,059 --> 00:17:28,920
[SPEAKER_00] Zato pazite da ne bi on sada godilo.

459
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,980
[SPEAKER_00] Da zapišeš sve,

460
00:17:29,980 --> 00:17:30,859
[SPEAKER_00] čuješ sve

461
00:17:30,859 --> 00:17:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] i onda staneš.

462
00:17:32,079 --> 00:17:35,240
[SPEAKER_00] I čekaš dok Ivančeš krene dalje.

463
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] To nije to.

464
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ti uzimaš ono što sam rekao,

465
00:17:39,460 --> 00:17:40,819
[SPEAKER_00] tek odnaka ti sam sebi kadaš,

466
00:17:40,819 --> 00:17:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] da, ja se Isuse odlučujem.

467
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:46,140
[SPEAKER_00] I drugo kad sebi kaže,

468
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:48,160
[SPEAKER_00] da, ja znam tko sam.

469
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se moraš reći,

470
00:17:49,079 --> 00:17:50,359
[SPEAKER_00] znam odakle dolazi.

471
00:17:50,359 --> 00:17:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam kamo idem.

472
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam tko je moja sudbina.

473
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:58,660
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko ljudi me ne ne pozna.

474
00:17:58,660 --> 00:18:00,839
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko mi ne može spasiti život.

475
00:18:00,839 --> 00:18:02,759
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko mi nije ni dao život.

476
00:18:02,759 --> 00:18:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko ne zna odakle dolazim na svijet.

477
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:07,319
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko ne zna šta je to smrt.

478
00:18:07,319 --> 00:18:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ima samo jedan koji mi je prijatelj.

479
00:18:09,619 --> 00:18:11,140
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je moj prijatelj.

480
00:18:11,140 --> 00:18:12,279
[SPEAKER_00] I zato znam tko sam.

481
00:18:12,279 --> 00:18:14,759
[SPEAKER_00] I sad si na duhovno razli.

482
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:18,819
[SPEAKER_00] I treće, baš moraš polako rukom

483
00:18:18,819 --> 00:18:21,700
[SPEAKER_00] i govoriti u ime otca i sina.

484
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:24,519
[SPEAKER_00] I dok to šapćući govoriš,

485
00:18:24,519 --> 00:18:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] da čuješ gotovo,

486
00:18:25,619 --> 00:18:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] tada se događa.

487
00:18:26,859 --> 00:18:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] Inače ne.

488
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ćeš ovdje sjediti u saludu.

489
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] Tebi se nudi bogati,

490
00:18:34,420 --> 00:18:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] božanski, nebeski.

491
00:18:37,740 --> 00:18:39,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj okus prekrasnih jela,

492
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] božanskih večera,

493
00:18:40,579 --> 00:18:42,140
[SPEAKER_00] ti ništa nisi okusio.

494
00:18:42,140 --> 00:18:44,259
[SPEAKER_00] I sjediš, prekriženi nogu

495
00:18:44,259 --> 00:18:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] i gledaš, ne znaš kućeš sa sobom.

496
00:18:45,859 --> 00:18:47,339
[SPEAKER_00] Zato moraš obavezno.

497
00:18:47,339 --> 00:18:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] To znači poći,

498
00:18:48,819 --> 00:18:50,140
[SPEAKER_00] kad ti počeš sebi govoriti.

499
00:18:50,140 --> 00:18:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] U ime otca i sina i duha svetoga.

500
00:18:55,539 --> 00:18:56,119
[UNKNOWN] Amen.

501
00:18:56,119 --> 00:18:57,740
[SPEAKER_00] Da ti se odlučio za Boga.

502
00:18:57,740 --> 00:18:58,640
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ti počeš govoriti,

503
00:18:58,640 --> 00:18:59,640
[SPEAKER_00] ti se odlučio.

504
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:00,279
[SPEAKER_00] To je tvoja odluka

505
00:19:00,279 --> 00:19:01,200
[SPEAKER_00] i ti za to govoriš.

506
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ti izlaziš iz sebe

507
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:03,680
[SPEAKER_00] i Bogu kažeš da.

508
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:06,220
[SPEAKER_00] U ime otca i sina i duha svetoga.

509
00:19:07,740 --> 00:19:11,200
[SPEAKER_00] Isto, četvrta točka,

510
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:11,980
[SPEAKER_00] ti baš moraš reći,

511
00:19:11,980 --> 00:19:14,140
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse, molim da ući.

512
00:19:14,140 --> 00:19:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] I dok to govoriš,

513
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,660
[SPEAKER_00] ti doživljavaš kako tvoja riječ.

514
00:19:16,660 --> 00:19:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] Zajesta, jer je duhovna,

515
00:19:18,420 --> 00:19:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] jer iz tvojega duha,

516
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,259
[SPEAKER_00] prelazi Isusu

517
00:19:20,259 --> 00:19:21,700
[SPEAKER_00] i kako Isusa doziva

518
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] i uvodi u tebe.

519
00:19:22,460 --> 00:19:23,819
[SPEAKER_00] Isus dolazi u tebe.

520
00:19:23,819 --> 00:19:24,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ti to doživljavaš.

521
00:19:24,839 --> 00:19:25,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to ne doživljavaš,

522
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne moliš kako treba.

523
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] Da dozivljavaš,

524
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] sad si s Isusom.

525
00:19:29,599 --> 00:19:32,700
[SPEAKER_00] To je srce počne drhtati od radosti.

526
00:19:32,700 --> 00:19:34,160
[SPEAKER_00] I za petu točku,

527
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse, pogledaj se.

528
00:19:35,119 --> 00:19:37,160
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledaj cijeli današnji dan,

529
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] včerašnji dan.

530
00:19:38,099 --> 00:19:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledaj moji prošli 150 godina,

531
00:19:40,619 --> 00:19:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] 30 godina,

532
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] 20, 60, 50.

533
00:19:43,119 --> 00:19:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledaj Isus.

534
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] Samo gledaš za Isusom.

535
00:19:45,579 --> 00:19:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kako Isus prvomatra kaže,

536
00:19:46,940 --> 00:19:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] zašto si ovo načinio?

537
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:50,240
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto nisi ovdje napravio bolje?

538
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:51,359
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto si se preio?

539
00:19:51,359 --> 00:19:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto si ovdje psovao?

540
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto si se poslađao?

541
00:19:54,420 --> 00:19:56,200
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto danas opće nisi molio?

542
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:58,640
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto jučer opće nisi čitao svetopisima?

543
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto si došao večeras?

544
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:06,180
[SPEAKER_00] Samo gledaj Isusa kako on to pregledava,

545
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] tvoje prostore.

546
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:09,200
[SPEAKER_00] Prostore to je duše

547
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] i kako reagira i kako ti govori.

548
00:20:12,579 --> 00:20:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kao što si ti govorio Isusu,

549
00:20:16,599 --> 00:20:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] sad on tebi govori,

550
00:20:17,539 --> 00:20:18,180
[SPEAKER_00] to se čuje,

551
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] njegova riječ.

552
00:20:19,079 --> 00:20:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] I ta riječ koju čuješ,

553
00:20:20,619 --> 00:20:21,319
[SPEAKER_00] šta te liječi?

554
00:20:21,319 --> 00:20:23,839
[SPEAKER_00] Njegova riječ.

555
00:20:23,839 --> 00:20:26,980
[SPEAKER_00] Te moraš,

556
00:20:26,980 --> 00:20:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je riječi,

557
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:29,339
[SPEAKER_00] bez riječi on ne dolazi.

558
00:20:29,339 --> 00:20:32,259
[SPEAKER_00] I ovo je sve riječi,

559
00:20:32,259 --> 00:20:33,240
[SPEAKER_00] sada moraš riječi,

560
00:20:33,319 --> 00:20:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] govoriti Bogu.

561
00:20:34,380 --> 00:20:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] Odvratite njegovu riječ,

562
00:20:37,119 --> 00:20:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] riječu,

563
00:20:38,039 --> 00:20:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] kada riječ Božja dolazi k tebi.

564
00:20:39,759 --> 00:20:41,180
[SPEAKER_00] A riječ Božja je Bog.

565
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kad on dobroši,

566
00:20:45,519 --> 00:20:46,359
[SPEAKER_00] ti ga gledaš,

567
00:20:46,359 --> 00:20:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] kadaš da ćeš otići,

568
00:20:47,380 --> 00:20:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] ne Isuse,

569
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:49,700
[SPEAKER_00] kao Marija Magdalena,

570
00:20:49,700 --> 00:20:50,920
[SPEAKER_00] zagrliću tvoje noge,

571
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,579
[SPEAKER_00] ne dam ti da odeš.

572
00:20:52,579 --> 00:20:54,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ostani Isuse,

573
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja ću opet biti isti

574
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,480
[SPEAKER_00] koji učer ako odeš.

575
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:58,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to mu reci,

576
00:20:58,339 --> 00:21:00,359
[SPEAKER_00] sad ostani, molim da.

577
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] ostani,

578
00:21:04,980 --> 00:21:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] ti znaš moje muke,

579
00:21:05,980 --> 00:21:07,660
[SPEAKER_00] ti znaš moje bolesti,

580
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:10,220
[SPEAKER_00] znaš moj pakao,

581
00:21:10,220 --> 00:21:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] kod kuće,

582
00:21:11,119 --> 00:21:12,160
[SPEAKER_00] na faksu,

583
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] poduzeću.

584
00:21:15,359 --> 00:21:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] molim da ostani u meni.

585
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je sada uvod u molitu,

586
00:21:22,039 --> 00:21:23,319
[SPEAKER_00] sad si ušao u molitu,

587
00:21:23,319 --> 00:21:25,099
[SPEAKER_00] to kao kad si ušao u more,

588
00:21:25,099 --> 00:21:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] zaronio si,

589
00:21:26,599 --> 00:21:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] sad si u Bogu.

590
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:28,740
[SPEAKER_00] E, šta sad?

591
00:21:28,740 --> 00:21:30,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sad je na tebi da plivaš.

592
00:21:30,980 --> 00:21:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] Sad je na tebi da se koprcaš,

593
00:21:34,079 --> 00:21:34,779
[SPEAKER_00] da naučiš plivaš.

594
00:21:34,779 --> 00:21:35,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ti pitaš Isaka,

595
00:21:35,980 --> 00:21:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] kako je tebi?

596
00:21:36,619 --> 00:21:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse, šta da rade?

597
00:21:40,220 --> 00:21:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse, ajmo sada ovim prijateljom

598
00:21:41,960 --> 00:21:42,859
[SPEAKER_00] da ih počnemo voljeti,

599
00:21:42,859 --> 00:21:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] daj baš da vidim

600
00:21:43,539 --> 00:21:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] koji su to ljudi ovdje.

601
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:46,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jo, Isuse,

602
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:47,779
[SPEAKER_00] samo nemoj da moram doći

603
00:21:47,779 --> 00:21:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] k njima blizu,

604
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] poludit ću.

605
